questiontext.text:
Sa se calculeze integrala trigonometrica folosind integrala in complex

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{0}^{\infty}\dfrac{1}{x^5+1}\,\mathrm{d}{x}\,. \]

Sa se calculeze integrala trigonometrica folosind integrala in complex

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{0}^{\infty}\dfrac{1}{x^7+1}\,\mathrm{d}{x}\,. \]

Sa se calculeze integrala trigonometrica folosind integrala in complex

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{0}^{\infty}\dfrac{x^2}{(x^6+1)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{x}\,. \]

Sa se calculeze integrala trigonometrica folosind integrala in complex

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{0}^{\infty}\dfrac{1}{(x^6+1)^3}\,\mathrm{d}{x}\,. \]

Sa se calculeze integrala trigonometrica folosind integrala in complex

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{0}^{\infty}\dfrac{x^4}{(x^2+1)^3}\,\mathrm{d}{x}\,. \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, \dfrac{\cos{(2z)}}{(z+i)(z-1)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z-\sqrt{3}|=2\,. \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, \dfrac{e^{\pi z}}{(z-2i)(z+1)}\,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z-\sqrt{5}|+|z+\sqrt{5}|=6\,. \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, \dfrac{3z+1}{(z-1)(z+i)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z-1+3i|=3\,. \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, \dfrac{\sin{(2z)}}{(z-i)(z+1)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z+\sqrt{3}|=2\,. \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, \dfrac{e^{-i\pi z}}{(z+2)(z-i)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z-i\sqrt{5}|+|z+i\sqrt{5}|=6\,. \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, \dfrac{2iz-5}{(z+1)(z-i)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z+1-3i|=3\,. \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, \dfrac{z^2-iz+1}{(z-2)(z+2i)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z-2+3i|=3\,. \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, \dfrac{e^{-i\pi z}+1}{(z+i)(z+1)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z-2i|=3\,. \]

Sa se determine punctele singulare si sa se calculeze reziduul in acele puncte functia \(f(z)\) : 

\[f(z)= \displaystyle\dfrac{(z-1) e^{1/2z}}{z+3}\,.  \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, \dfrac{\exp{(-z)}}{(z+2)^4}\,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z+2|=1\,. \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, \dfrac{\exp{(-1/z)}}{(z+2)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z|=\dfrac{3}{2}\,. \]

Sa se calculeze integrala reala folosind integrala in complex

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\dfrac{\sin (3x)}{x^2-2x+2}\,\mathrm{d}{x}\,. \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, z^4 e^{1/z} \,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z|=1\,. \]

Sa se calculeze integrala trigonometrica folosind integrala in complex

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\dfrac{x^3+x}{x^6+1}\,\mathrm{d}{x}\,. \]

Sa se calculeze integrala reala folosind integrala in complex

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\dfrac{x\sin (5x)}{x^2+2x+10}\,\mathrm{d}{x}\,. \]

Sa se calculeze integrala reala folosind integrala in complex

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\dfrac{\cos (2x)}{x^2-2x+2}\,\mathrm{d}{x}\,. \]

Sa se calculeze integrala reala folosind integrala in complex

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\dfrac{x^4+2x}{(x^2+1)(x^3+1)}\,\mathrm{d}{x}\,. \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, \dfrac{z^2-iz+1}{(z-2)(z+2i)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z-2+3i|=3\,. \]

Sa se calculeze integrala reala folosind integrala in complex

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\dfrac{x^3\sin (4x)}{(x^2+4)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{x}\,. \]

Folosind teorema reziduurilor, sa se calculeze integrala 

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{\gamma}\, \dfrac{e^{-i\pi z}+1}{(z+i)(z+1)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{z} ~,\quad\gamma:|z-2i|=3\,. \]

Sa se calculeze integrala reala folosind integrala in complex

\[ I=\displaystyle\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\dfrac{x^2\cos (4x)}{(x^2+9)^2}\,\mathrm{d}{x}\,. \]
